熱力學一



















ESS2400 Thermodynamics I, 熱力學一










Course Description:
            1 Introductory concepts and definition (T , P , units , etc . .....)
            2 Energy & First law of Thermodynamics (Work , heat , energy transfer etc.)
3 Properties of a pure , simple compressible substance (State principle , p-v-T relation , thermodynamics properties , ideal gas model etc .....)
4 Control volume energy analysis (Conservation of mass , conservation of energy , steady state , transient state etc.....)
5 Second law of thermodynamics (Second law , reversible , irreversible , maximum performance measures for power , refrigeration , and heat    
   pump cycles operating between two reservoirs , Carnot cycle etc .....)
6 Entropy ( Clauses inequality , definition , isentropic process , isentropic efficiencies of turbines , nozzles , compressors and pumps , and heat
   transfer and work in internal reversible , steady state flow processes etc .....)
7 Thermodynamics relations for a simple compressible substance , Equation of state , Maxwell relation , constructing table of thermodynamics
   properties , generalized charts for enthalpy and entropy , p-v-T relations for gas mixture
　




課程說明：
            基本定義與觀念 , 純粹物質之熱力學性質的決定 , 熱力學第一定律--閉合與開放系統 , 熱力學第二定律--熵及能量之做功潛力
             













